<br>
Then teh Cow decided she just *had* to ding that day, since she was so close anyways.  So Fenn ran out and pulled a couple, and I went out and pulled a couple, and I think teh Ssas and Cow pulled one or two wandering mobs back at camp, soooo.........<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.boomspeed.com/bagapics/ew_1.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
